items.name: Pastel SushiToon
items.description:
This model takes my previous model of "SushiToonScape" and merges it with "JewelDefactaPastel11" to create a more artistic watercolor like style to the generations.

How to use

- Clip skip: 2

- CFG scale: 8

- Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras,

- Sampling Steps : 20-25

- Upscaler (Hires. fix): R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B, 4x-AnimeSharp, 4x-UltraSharp

- Hires steps: 14

- Denoising strength: 0.5

- Upscale by: 1.5+

- Positive: (high quality, masterpiece), ... other quality tags work but too many skews pictures

- Negative: (low quality, signature, watermark), ...

- Use aDetailer to fix the faces

  • Use face_yolov8n.pt

Credits

JewelDefactaPastel11 @himizumenou

Through a carefully crafted balance of cutting-edge AI technology and adherence to ethical principles, the Prefix Real Cart model aims to redefine the AI content generation landscape. By enabling women and supporters of female empowerment to be part of the AI revolution, this model paves the way for a more diverse, inclusive, and exciting digital future.

In conclusion, the Prefix Real Cart stable diffusion model is a remarkable achievement in the world of AI-generated content. Dedicated to empowering women and celebrating beauty in all its forms, this model serves as a powerful tool for creative expression and personal growth. With its commitment to user safety and inclusivity, the Prefix Real Cart is not just a model but a stepping stone towards a more equitable and dynamic AI ecosystem. items.name: Nordrin_little（诺德琳little）
items.description:
强烈建议使用EasyNegative作为负面提示词

  • 注意，3.0版本为2.5版本的微调，这并不意味着3.0一定比2.5强

    主要差异：

    衣物细节：-

    眼睛的细节：++

    头部宽度：-

    饱和度：+

    欧派大小：+ ～(￣▽￣～)(～￣▽￣)～

该模型是Nordrin（诺德琳）模型的分支，little模型基本解决了Nordrin的色彩问题（或许我该为失去一种独特的风格而悲伤）同时，尽最大可能的保留了原模型的特征，但代价是她看起来，有那么一点点.....little？算了，至少她足够可爱~

推荐参数

迭代步数 (Steps)：20-40

采样方法 (Sampler)：

DPM++ 2M SDE

DPM++ 2M

提示词引导系数 (CFG Scale)：7-12

建议打开高清修复以提高画面质量：重绘幅度0.55-0.6

放大算法随意

该模型属于偶然产物，存在许多不足，还请见谅

Here is the translation in English:

It is highly recommended to use EasyNegative as a negative prompt

Note, version 3.0 is a fine-tuning of version 2.5, which does not mean that 3.0 is necessarily better than 2.5

Main differences:

Clothing details: -

Eye details: ++

Head width: -

Saturation: +

Bust size: + ～(￣▽￣～)(～￣▽￣)～

This model is a branch of the Nordrin model. The little model basically solves the color problem of Nordrin (maybe I should be sad for losing a unique style) while retaining the original features of the model as much as possible. But the price is that she looks, a little bit… little? Well, at least she is cute enough~

Recommended parameters

Iteration steps (Steps): 20-40

Sampling method (Sampler):

DPM++ 2M SDE

DPM++ 2M

Prompt guidance coefficient (CFG Scale): 7-12

It is recommended to turn on HD repair to improve image quality: repaint range 0.55-0.6

Magnification algorithm is optional

This model is an accidental product, there are many shortcomings, please forgive me

Gives dudes a big raging hard-on in their pants.

items.name: Workshop_semi_cartoon
items.description:
大家好，我是神秘高手K。

简单色色块搭配简单的线条，嗯，简单其实就是一种美，尤其是看腻了ai繁杂的细节。

来，试一试“工坊半卡通Workshop_semi_cartoon”

如果你是儿插画师，相信它一定会给你一些创意与灵感。

如果你是卡通爱好者，也不容错过。

生成建议：

1.使用DPM++ 2M,20-30步即可。

Eta 噪声种子偏移(ENSD - Eta noise seed delta，建议值31337)

Simple color blocks paired with simple lines, um, simplicity is actually a form of beauty, especially when tired of the intricate details of AI.

Come on, give it a try with the 'Workshop Semi Cartoon Workshop_semi_cartoon'

If you are an illustrator, I believe it will definitely give you some creativity and inspiration.

If you are an cartoon enthusiast, don't miss it either.

Generate suggestions:

1. Using DPM++2M, take 20-30 steps.

Eta noise seed offset (ENSD - Eta noise seed delta, recommended value 31337)

Negative prompt words can be used: lowres, bad anatomy, bad hands, text, error, missing fingers, extra digit, fewer digits, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, signature, watermark, username, blurry,nsfw,

Venez essayer « Workshop semi Cartoon Workshop semi Cartoon »

Si vous êtes un illustrateur enfant, croyez que cela vous donnera certainement de la créativité et de l'inspiration.

Si vous êtes un amateur de dessins animés, ne manquez pas non plus.

Bloques de color simples con líneas simples, bueno, la simplicidad es en realidad una belleza, especialmente cansado de ver los complicados detalles de ai.

Aquí, pruebe "workshop semi Cartoon Workshop semi cartoon"

Si eres ilustrador, creo que te dará alguna creatividad e inspiración.

Si eres un entusiasta de los dibujos animados, no puedes perderte.

Generar recomendaciones:

Desplazamiento de semillas de ruido ETA (ensd - ETA Noise Seed delta, valor recomendado 31.337)

 Простые цветовые блоки с простыми линиями, ну, простота на самом деле является красотой, особенно устала видеть сложные детали ai. 

 Приходите, попробуйте "Workshop semi cartoon".

items.name: Heterothallism
items.description:
This LoRA is applied particularly to distinguish heterothallic fungi, which require two compatible partners to produce sexual spores, from homothallic ones, which are capable of sexual reproduction from a single organism.

The Bianchetto truffle is a heterothallic Ascomycete living in symbiotic association with trees and shrubs.

Slime molds were formerly classified as fungi but are no longer considered part of that kingdom. Although not forming a single monophyletic clade, they are grouped within the paraphyletic group Protista.

If you don't want to see Scoby, type kombucha at the negative prompt.
